{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/endings/layout,_N_T_/endings/page,_N_T_/endings"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/endings/__PAGE__","/endings","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"dark\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/favicon.png\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/hero-corridor.jpg\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/favicon-32x32.png\" as=\"image\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/08m9azn6wt-jz.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/00gq-v0e07i1q.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0bymg5d-lqs0o.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07lhk_q6pmm3r.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-134gd3wlo5u4g.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/01xlw8hd842-c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0zhq~bpzm6_qm.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/16cnkn.3u5-c6.js\" async=\"\"></script><script async=\"\" src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-3GS2W560EC\"></script><script async=\"\" src=\"https://plausible.shipsolo.io/js/pa-ew39StHckGexwKZs37REB.js\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Creepster&amp;family=Epilogue:wght@600;700;800&amp;family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&amp;family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500&amp;display=swap\" as=\"style\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap\" as=\"style\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><title>Freak Circus Endings Guide (2026) | All Endings, Routes, Requirements &amp; Explained</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Complete Freak Circus endings guide. All 8+ endings explained: unlock conditions, step-by-step walkthroughs, requirements, rewards, and fan interpretations. Covers Pierrot, Harlequin, Doctor, and Columbina endings.\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"Freak Circus Hub\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Freak Circus endings,Freak Circus endings guide,ending guide,routes,requirements,explained,how to unlock,ending walkthrough,unlock ending,Pierrot endings,Harlequin endings,Doctor endings,Columbina endings,true ending,secret ending,hidden ending,canon ending,Eternal Silence,Corrupted Data,Columbina&#x27;s Truth,Grand Finale,all endings,ending order,ending timeline\"/><meta name=\"creator\" content=\"Freak Circus Hub\"/><meta name=\"publisher\" content=\"Freak Circus Hub\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><meta name=\"googlebot\" content=\"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://freak-circus.com/endings\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Freak Circus Endings Guide (2026) | All Endings, Routes, Requirements &amp; Explained\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Complete Freak Circus endings guide. All 8+ endings explained with unlock conditions, walkthroughs, and requirements.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://freak-circus.com/endings\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Freak Circus Hub\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Freak Circus Endings Guide (2026) | All Endings, Routes, Requirements &amp; Explained\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Complete Freak Circus endings guide. All endings, routes, requirements, and explained.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/Logo.png\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/Logo.png\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Creepster&amp;family=Epilogue:wght@600;700;800&amp;family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&amp;family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/><script>\n          window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n          function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n          gtag('js', new Date());\n          gtag('config', 'G-3GS2W560EC');\n        </script><script>\n          window.plausible = window.plausible || function() {\n            (window.plausible.q = window.plausible.q || []).push(arguments)\n          };\n          window.plausible.init = window.plausible.init || function(i) {\n            window.plausible.o = i || {};\n          };\n          window.plausible.init();\n        </script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"font-sans antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"grain-overlay\"></div><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-surface\"><nav class=\"fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b-2 border-primary-container shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgba(122,30,30,0.5)] flex justify-between items-center px-4 md:px-16 py-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary drop-shadow-[2px_2px_0px_#7A1E1E] tracking-tight scale-90 origin-left\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/favicon.png\" alt=\"Freak Circus Hub\" class=\"w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-sm\"/>FREAK CIRCUS HUB</a><div class=\"hidden md:flex gap-6 items-center\"><a class=\"transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary\" href=\"/characters\">Characters</a><a class=\"transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary\" href=\"/walkthroughs\">Walkthroughs</a><a class=\"transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-primary font-bold\" href=\"/endings\">Endings</a><a class=\"transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary\" href=\"/theories\">Theories</a><a class=\"transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary\" href=\"/lore\">Lore Archive</a><a class=\"relative group bg-blood text-surface px-7 py-2.5 border-2 border-blood shadow-[4px_4px_0px_#000] active:translate-x-1 active:translate-y-1 active:shadow-none transition-all font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary hover:border-primary hover:shadow-[5px_5px_0px_#000]\" href=\"https://freak-circus.com/play-online\"><span class=\"relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-block w-2 h-2 bg-surface rounded-full animate-pulse\"></span><span class=\"font-bold text-sm\">PLAY NOW</span></span></a></div><button class=\"md:hidden text-primary\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-3xl\">menu</span></button></nav><section class=\"bg-surface min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col justify-center pt-8 pb-16 px-4 md:px-16 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0\"><img src=\"/hero-corridor.jpg\" alt=\"Corridor\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-surface/80 via-surface/60 to-surface\"></div></div><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full relative z-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-8\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-3 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">BRANCH FAILED</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-3 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">TIMELINE COLLAPSED</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-3 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">MEMORY RETAINED</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-3 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">ROUTE CORRUPTION DETECTED</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-8 mb-8\"><div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary\">14</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Known Endings</div></div></div><h1 class=\"font-[Creepster] text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-primary mb-6\">Every Ending<br/>Hides Another Story</h1><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-2xl mb-8\">Explore every known route, hidden finale, corrupted branch, and timeline anomaly discovered inside The Freak Circus.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"px-6 py-3 border border-primary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-surface transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm uppercase\" href=\"#archive\">Explore All Endings</a><a class=\"px-6 py-3 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm uppercase\" href=\"#unverified\">Investigate Hidden Routes</a></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-12 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6\">Endings Guide Contents</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider\">All Endings</div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#categories\">├ <!-- -->Good Endings</a><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#categories\">├ <!-- -->Bad Endings</a><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#categories\">├ <!-- -->True Ending</a><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#categories\">├ <!-- -->Secret Ending</a><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#categories\">├ <!-- -->Hidden Ending</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider\">Character Endings</div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#archive\">├ <!-- -->Pierrot Endings</a><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#archive\">├ <!-- -->Harlequin Endings</a><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#archive\">├ <!-- -->Doctor Endings</a><a class=\"block text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm py-1\" href=\"#archive\">├ <!-- -->Columbina Endings</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">The Complete Ending Guide</h2><div class=\"space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant text-sm\"><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">How many endings exist?</h3><p>The community has confirmed 8 endings across all character routes, with 6 additional endings under investigation or unverified. The exact total remains unknown — data miners continue to find references to unused endings in game files, and the community suspects there may be endings that require specific combinations of previous completions to unlock.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which ending is considered the true ending?</h3><p>No single ending is universally accepted as the &quot;true ending.&quot; The community theory suggests that the true ending requires completing all four character routes in a specific order, with Columbina&#x27;s three-loop storyline being the final piece. However, this remains unverified. Some players argue that the Corrupted Data ending — found only in unused files — represents the intended conclusion that was cut during development.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which ending is hardest to unlock?</h3><p>Columbina&#x27;s Truth requires perfect alignment of all dialogue choices across three consecutive loops. Any deviation — even a single incorrect choice — causes a complete reset. The Corrupted Data ending may be impossible to unlock legitimately; no player has verified conditions, and it may be a debug remnant or intentionally unreachable content.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which endings require replaying the game?</h3><p>Four endings require replay awareness: Eternal Silence (requires completing one other route first), Columbina&#x27;s Truth (requires three loops), The Doctor&#x27;s Note (requires finding files across multiple playthroughs), and Harlequin&#x27;s Laughter (requires specific comedic choices that only become available after seeing her standard ending). The game tracks your history across saves using a hidden counter at offset 0x4A20.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Which endings remain unverified?</h3><p>Three endings remain unverified by the community: Corrupted Data (found in files but never unlocked), White Room (mentioned in patch notes but never found), and Null Route (a branch with no characters that soft-locks after 5 minutes). These may be cut content, debug remnants, or intentionally hidden endings that require conditions the community has not yet discovered.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">All Endings Table</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">Complete ending guide with unlock conditions, requirements, and rewards for every ending</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/20\"><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Ending</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Character</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Difficulty</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Type</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Unlock Conditions</th><th class=\"text-left p-3 text-foreground\">Rewards</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">The Grand Finale</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Normal</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Canon</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Complete Harlequin route with standard dialogue choices. No special conditions required.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">CG: Harlequin&#x27;s final bow. Achievement: &#x27;The Show Must Go On&#x27;.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Smile For Me</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Normal</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Canon</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Accept Pierrot&#x27;s offer during the garden scene in Act III.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">CG: Pierrot&#x27;s smile. Achievement: &#x27;Smile For Me&#x27;.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">The Doctor&#x27;s Note</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">The Doctor</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Hard</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Secret</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Find all 5 hidden medical files before the final encounter.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">CG: The Doctor&#x27;s handwritten note. Achievement: &#x27;Medical History&#x27;.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Eternal Silence</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Pierrot</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Hard</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Secret</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Refuse every major dialogue interaction during the final act. Screen stays black for 4 minutes.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">No CG. Post-credits narration only. Achievement: &#x27;Eternal Silence&#x27;.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Columbina&#x27;s Truth</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Columbina</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Very Hard</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Secret</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Perfect alignment of all dialogue choices across three loops. Any deviation resets to Loop 1.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">CG: The fourth door opening. Achievement: &#x27;Columbina&#x27;s Truth&#x27;.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">White Room</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Unknown</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Impossible</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">False</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Mentioned in patch notes 1.03. Conditions unknown. The Doctor describes it in Scene 7.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Unknown.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Corrupted Data</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">???</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Impossible</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Corrupted</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Found only in modified game files. Screen displays raw hex before crash.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">None. Game crashes after hex display.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-outline/10\"><td class=\"p-3 text-foreground font-bold\">Harlequin&#x27;s Laughter</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant\">Harlequin</td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Hidden</span></td><td class=\"p-3\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Joke</span></td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">Select every comedic option in a single playthrough.</td><td class=\"p-3 text-on-surface-variant text-xs max-w-xs\">CG: Harlequin laughing. Achievement: &#x27;Harlequin&#x27;s Laughter&#x27;.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">Ending Types</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">How The Freak Circus categorizes its conclusions — from standard resolutions to corrupted data</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-xl font-bold text-foreground\">Canon Endings</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">2<!-- --> endings</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed\">The standard conclusions for each character route. These endings resolve the main narrative threads and are achievable on the first playthrough without special requirements. The Grand Finale (Harlequin) and Smile For Me (Pierrot) are the two canon endings most players see on their initial playthrough.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-xl font-bold text-foreground\">Secret Endings</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">3<!-- --> endings</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed\">Hidden conclusions that require specific conditions, replay awareness, or sequence dependencies. Eternal Silence requires refusing all dialogue for three scenes. The Doctor&#x27;s Note requires finding five hidden medical files. Columbina&#x27;s Truth requires perfect alignment across three loops. These endings reveal deeper narrative layers.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-xl font-bold text-foreground\">Corrupted Endings</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">2<!-- --> endings</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed\">Endings found in unused game files or mentioned in patch notes but never officially unlocked. Corrupted Data displays raw hex before crashing. White Room is referenced by The Doctor in Scene 7 but has never been found. These may be cut content, debug remnants, or intentionally hidden.</p></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-3\"><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-xl font-bold text-foreground\">Joke Endings</h3><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary border border-primary/30 px-2 py-1\">1<!-- --> endings</span></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed\">Lighthearted or absurd conclusions that subvert the game&#x27;s horror tone. Harlequin&#x27;s Laughter requires selecting every comedic option in a single playthrough. These endings provide relief from the main narrative&#x27;s intensity and often contain fourth-wall-breaking humor.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"archive\" class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\">